Differences between NEdit and NEdit Plus:

* Definable File, Edit, and Search menus.
* Drag'n Drop Tabs (Motif only) and move Tabs left and right.
* Open Previous enhancements.
* list_multisel_dialog() function.
* $loaded_tags/tips_files and $marks arrays.
* Backlight macro support. (Disabled in NEdit since v5.4).
* Open Selected allows for spaces in the file name.
* SH background coloring beyond newlines possible.

